original_title: โซตัสเอสเดอะซีรีส์
overview: Fast forward 2 years from the events in SOTUS: The Series, Kongphop is now the head hazer in his faculty, while Arthit works at a company called Ocean Electric. During Kongphop's final year, he needs to find an internship company and requests to work alongside Arthit over his family's company, unbeknownst to Arthit. After an outing with the company, tensions rise between the two, and both will have to decide their future.
title: โซตัสเอสเดอะซีรีส์
